# Local Environment Settings

## Ngrok

- Domain: `<your-ngrok-domain>.ngrok-free.app`
- Port: `21864`

## Slack Workspace

- Workspace: `<your-workspace>.slack.com`

## Key Channel IDs

| Environment Variable | Channel ID | Purpose |
|----------------------|------------|---------|
| `CHANNEL_SANDBOX` | `<channel-id>` | Sandbox channel (best for testing) |
